{"tid":2179571,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"自願檢疫屬情緒勒索 陶傑︰請驗高官大腦","createTime":"2020-08-29T08:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T08:29:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56396aeeb5e5de8c7f78fc51b1e62026c5f4dc54","tid":2179571,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_757026_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_757026_0&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=dfc246ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_757026_0&h=f5943269\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_757026_0</a><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯瑞典及美國的佛羅里達州都先後發現，就算以北歐和美國的醫療水準去應付武肺病毒而展開檢疫，都發現有很多個案是驗錯，陰性驗錯為陽性。在這方面來說，瑞典的衛生署和佛羅里達州的衛生部都有這樣的公布，以及說很麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯檢疫完並不代表免疫。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯所以要全民接受檢疫為一個勒索的條件來放寬限聚令，陳肇始局長是極之不道德，而且是極之卑劣的。<br />\n<br />\n希望蘋果見到<br />\n早啲放哩條片上youtube"},{"pid":"5e26a4221d256545fd3dde50492e28346cb81526","tid":2179571,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:17:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">陳肇真係應該驗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b05b8e31844a8ed25aca9a200144e6cca129a1f4","tid":2179571,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e26a4221d256545fd3dde50492e28346cb81526","tid":2179571,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:17:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">陳肇真係應該驗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:35:10.0